{"tid":563402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（年度Interview)往惡姨丈家拜年起爭拗　15歲姨甥被提早「開年」","createTime":"2018-02-17T01:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T06:48:56.000Z","uid":19552,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"abffcef2cc4dafa33549403b51654076e609eab0","tid":563402,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:12:49.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=JIlxGgzyIxv6YoIyY9fM5kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=dcb83e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】15歲姨甥拜年起衝突，慘被惡姨丈提早「開年」！一名15歲姓方男童與其48歲姓葉母親，昨(16日)晚9時許，往位於屯門山景邨姨丈家拜年，期間因家事問題與姨丈發生爭執，有人一度情緒激動，毆傷男童並出言恐嚇他，遇襲男童母親制止不果，致電報案，姨丈見已報警即奪門逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，將頸部受傷男童送院治理，經初步調查，案件改列作刑事恐嚇及襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由屯門警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"45d8c6c070e8811a8f0f60c4cb7f0b9a6e4599fd","tid":563402,"uid":29314,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:13:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾！<br />\n<br />\n15歲人咁大個都打唔贏個廢中！"},{"pid":"59ff7a4392840b93a53ee087e9b561e54ee768df","tid":563402,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"遇襲男童母親制止不果，致電報案，姨丈見已報警即奪門逃去。<br />\n<br />\n著草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0506bf76ed5d2ae5a36014ea281556c7cd6b3ce5","tid":563402,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:15:43.000Z","msg":"老貓打貓仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cdd03a033b3f82b5d1c2bb534ac051abb747e6","tid":563402,"uid":34760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:16:02.000Z","msg":